name: Câu
description: Mid-Autumn Festival when I was a child, I ran after colorful unicorns, carried lanterns from the beginning of the village to the end of the village, I liked paper lanterns more than electric lights, so every year I was the first to set fire to the lanterns. . Every year, it is a festival to open a box of cakes with salted eggs or green beans. I always imagine people riding something weirder in the mid-autumn festival so I drew this picture :)))))
